# Rock Paper Scissors Game

This is a simple Rock Paper Scissors game implemented using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to play against the computer and view the outcome on the webpage.

## How to Play
1. Open the `index.html` file in your web browser.
2. Click on one of the buttons to select your choice: Rock, Paper, or Scissors.
3. The computer will randomly choose its option.
4. The result of the game (win, lose, or tie) will be displayed on the screen.

## Features
- Play Rock Paper Scissors against the computer.
- Visual representation of choices with buttons and icons.
- Responsive design for different screen sizes.
- Easy-to-understand interface with clear game results.

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

